      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミソなんて
その辺で買ってきたのじゃダメなのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it not good enough to just
buy miso from a local shop?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>奴の要求は
この洞窟の奥に眠る
伝説のミソを取ってこい、というものだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The demand is to retrieve the legendary miso
resting within the innermost part of this cave.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もし他のミソで誤魔化そうとすれば
おそらく彼女は無惨にも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I try to deceive her with fake miso,
most likely, she'll face a tragic end...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>くすぐられるだけ、なんだけどな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think she's just trying to amuse herself...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure about this.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
